com.google.code.mybatis.generator.plugins
Class CriteriaBuilderPlugin

java.lang.Object
  org.mybatis.generator.api.PluginAdapter
      com.google.code.mybatis.generator.plugins.CriteriaBuilderPlugin
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.mybatis.generator.api.Plugin
public class CriteriaBuilderPlugin
extends org.mybatis.generator.api.PluginAdapter

Adds "builder-style" to the generated XXXExample classes. Thus inner XXXExample.Criteria class will become an additional "example()" method the returns the example instance itself.
Example configuration:

 <generatorConfiguration>
  <context ...>

      <plugin type="com.google.code.mybatis.generator.plugins.CriteriaBuilderPlugin"/>
      ...

  </context>
 </generatorConfiguration>
